snippet.title: John  Depp with Amber Heard won best Actor with his famous theme Pirates of the Caribbean
snippet.description:
Among his numerous competitive awards, he has won the Screen Actors Guild Award for Outstanding Actor in a Leading Role for Pirates of the Caribbean: The Curse of the Black Pearl (2003), and the Golden Globe Award for Best Actor - Motion Picture Musical or Comedy for Sweeney Todd: The Demon Barber of Fleet Street. He is also a three-time Academy Award nominee.
